        "path: package.json:58-65 :: the normal repo gate is `typecheck`, `test`, and package verification.",
        "path: extensions/agent-browser/index.ts:102-108 :: `buildMissingBinaryMessage` defines the user-facing error text.",
        "workflow: `rg -n \"required but was not found on PATH|buildMissingBinaryMessage|ENOENT|--version\" test/agent-browser.test.ts extensions/agent-browser/index.ts docs/TOOL_CONTRACT.md docs/IMPLEMENTATION_PLAN.md README.md` :: observed the ENOENT branch exists in implementation/docs, while the concrete execution coverage in `test/agent-browser.test.ts` explicitly exercises `--version` inspection rather than the missing-binary path."
      ],
      "plan": [
