        "npm run verify"
      ],
      "evidence": [
        "path: extensions/agent-browser/lib/results/envelope.ts:91-113 :: fallback failures collapse to generic exit-code text when no stderr or usable envelope error exists",
        "path: test/agent-browser.test.ts:1279-1299 :: tests currently accept the generic fallback branch instead of protecting a more actionable error contract",
        "workflow: npx tsx --eval 'import { getAgentBrowserErrorText } from \"./extensions/agent-browser/lib/results/envelope.ts\"; ...' :: expected command-aware failure text :: actual output was only generic exit-code messages"
